# Frontend Architecture

## Entry point
`main.tsx` wraps `<App>` in `<IslandSceneShell>` (scene backdrop + palms + day/night vars) inside `React.StrictMode`. The scene is always visible — including behind the login screen.

## Auth & routing
- `App.tsx` owns shared state, the cross-page `apiFetch` loaders, and the top-level page switch.
- `isAuthenticated` starts `null` → `LoginScreen` until resolved.
- Routing is **React Router** (`react-router`): the URL is the source of truth. `App.tsx` derives `page: PageId` from the path via `pageFromPath(location.pathname)` (`lib/routes.ts`); navigation goes through `navigateToPage(next)` → `navigate(pathForPage(next))`. Each routed page is **lazy-loaded** (`lazy()` + `<Suspense>`); unknown path → `null` page → `NotFoundPage`.
- Page<->path map + helpers (`pathForPage`, `pageFromPath`, `pathForIslander`, `pathForForumThread`, `pathForGame`, `activityHref`) live in `apps/web/src/lib/routes.ts`. Forums and Admin parse their own sub-paths internally.
- `isAdmin = profileData?.roleNames.includes("Parent")`.
- Pages **may** call `apiFetch` directly for their own data (e.g. `Achievements`, `Community`, `CommunityLeaderboard`, `CrewAchievements`, `Forums`, `IslanderProfile`). `App.tsx` still owns the shared/polled loaders and passes that data + callbacks down as props.

## Pages (apps/web/src/pages/)
Page set is driven by `lib/routes.ts` (`PAGE_PATHS` / `pageFromPath`). All pages below are real/implemented (API-backed) unless a note says otherwise.

| Page (id) | Path | Status |
|-----------|------|--------|
| `Home` (`home`) | `/` | Real — featured game, friends online, activity feed (capped, "View full feed" → Community), drift log. |
| `Games` (`games`) | `/games` | Real — game nights + RSVP, session composer recs, Steam news, crew wishlist. Note: stream drawer (`STREAMS_MOCK`) + mode chips are local-state-only. |
| `GamingNews` (`games-news`) | `/games/news` | Real — AI-curated "Gaming News" feed. |
| `Library` (`library`) | `/library` | Real — full crew library + owner avatars + MINE badge; detail drawer via `?game=` query param. |
| `Community` (`community`) | `/community` | Real — hero, crew carousel, activity timeline, forums row (`/forums/categories`), events (wired to `gameNights`), Nuggies leaderboard (`/nuggies/leaderboard`). Clubs/Clips were cut. |
| `Forums` (`community-forums`) | `/forums`, `/forums/thread/:id` | Real — categories/threads/posts/search via `/forums/*`; parses its own sub-paths. |
| `CommunityLeaderboard` (`community-leaderboard`) | `/community/leaderboard` | Real — `/nuggies/leaderboard`. |
| `CrewAchievements` (`crew-achievements`) | `/achievements` | Real — `/steam/crew-achievements`. |
| `Achievements` / Nuggies (`nuggies`) | `/nuggies` | Real — balance, daily claim, shop, inventory, loans, leaderboard (`/nuggies/me`, `/shop`, `/daily`, `/inventory`, `/loan`, `/leaderboard`). |
| `CasinoPage` (`nuggies-casino`) | `/nuggies/casino` | Real — Nuggies casino games. |
| `NuggiesHistory` (`nuggies-history`) | `/nuggies/history` | Real — transaction history. |
| `Milestones` (`nuggies-milestones`) | `/nuggies/milestones` | Real — milestone/rank progress. |
| `TideCheck` (`tide-check`) | `/tide-check` | Real — game-night tide check. |
| `IslanderProfile` (`islander-profile`) | `/islanders/:userId` | Real — per-member public profile. |
| `Profile` (`profile`) | `/profile` | Real — MeProfile, owned games + exclusion toggles (server-persisted via `/profile/steam-exclusions`). |
| `Settings` (`settings`) | `/settings` | Real — Steam link/sync, visibility, feature opt-in. |
| `Admin` (`admin`) | `/admin`, `/admin/*` | Real — sub-routed admin (dashboard, news, economy, people, ai, system, discord, games) under `pages/admin/*`; parses its own sub-paths. |

## Components (apps/web/src/components/)
- `Topbar` — `position: fixed` glass header (62px spacer div in App.tsx); global search is local state only (not wired to API)
- `UserMenu` — day/night toggle via `useDayNight`, Steam panel, profile/admin links, logout
- `SteamOnboarding` — post-login modal; skip state persisted per user in `localStorage`
- `steam.tsx` — Steam brand components + `steamSignInUrl()` pointing to `/steam/openid/start`

## Background sync intervals (App.tsx)
- Featured/activity/news: every 5 min
- Guild member sync: every 1 min
- Game nights list: every 20s (on Games page)
- Selected night refresh: every 15s
- Steam sync: every 10 min (when linked)

## Key types (apps/web/src/types.ts)
`PageId`, `MeProfile`, `GuildMember`, `GameNight`, `GameNightAttendee`, `CrewOwnedGame`, `CrewWishlistGame`, `FeaturedRecommendation`, `GameNewsItem`, `ActivityEvent`, `NewsCard`, `ServerSetting`
